        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事米蘭：並未向川普承諾會在利率決策中投反對票",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Stephen Miran Photographer: Daniel Heuer/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fQxTqz3_Dibo9h1EWk4Ajw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a6ceec9ccc569e4ac6f43988137dd011\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Stephen Miran Photographer: Daniel Heuer/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>理事斯蒂芬·米蘭表示，自本周聯儲會政策會議以來，他還沒有與川普交談過，也沒有向總統承諾在利率問題上會以特定方式投票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我將基於自己對數據的解讀、對經濟的解讀，進行獨立分析。這就是我將要做的，也是我唯一會做的，」米蘭周五在接受CNBC採訪時表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">身為川普的盟友，米蘭正從白宮經濟顧問委員會主席一職休無薪假。這種不尋常的情況引起了民主黨人的批評，他們稱這一安排對央行的獨立性構成威脅。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dddd41c5-43ed-3fc0-9f90-4154b8378245-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會本周決定將基準利率下調25個基點。米蘭對此持異議，主張一次性下調50個基點。這是他在周二就任聯儲會理事後參加的首場政策會議。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"聯儲會理事斯蒂芬·米蘭攝影師：DanielHeuer/彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TwIYmqHVbBF9Bbb1_dKhrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/dd7019cd3b70949f3f51dcca903da375\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聯儲會理事斯蒂芬·米蘭攝影師：DanielHeuer/彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">米蘭表示，川普周二早上致電祝賀他獲得確認，但補充說，總統沒有和他談及他將如何在會議上投票，而且自那以後也沒有和他交流過。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「他沒有要求我採取任何具體行動。我也沒有承諾採取任何特定行動，」Miran說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">決策者還在會後發布了新的季度利率路徑預測。米蘭周五表示，其中那個預計今年累計降息150個基點的「離群」預測正出自他本人。他強調，這一預測「是基於我的經濟分析，這也是我將繼續堅持的」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年，隨著川普加力施壓聯儲會，獨立性已成為聯儲會面臨的一大挑戰。川普正試圖解雇聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克，這一前所未有的舉動導致最高法院即將作出一項事關重大的裁決。川普還不斷施壓聯儲會主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾和其他政策制定者大幅降低利率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為本周會議上唯一持不同意見的官員，米蘭表示希望他在理事會任職期間能夠成為一個有影響力的聲音。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他說：「我將在未來幾周和幾個月內提出我的論點，我希望在此過程中能夠說服我的一些同事。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他補充說，包括庫克在內的所有同事都「非常歡迎」他。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">米蘭周五淡化了對關稅引發通膨的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我沒有看到關稅導致任何實質性通膨。我沒有看到有證據表明這種情況已經發生，」他說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Miran Says He Didn’t Promise Trump He’d Dissent on Rates</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E7%B1%B3%E8%98%AD-%E4%B8%A6%E6%9C%AA%E5%90%91%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E6%B1%BA%E7%AD%96%E4%B8%AD%E6%8A%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%A5%A8-164050851.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-20 01:35:39",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國最高法院要求聯儲會理事庫克9月25日前做出回應",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國最高法院首席大法官約翰·羅伯茨要求聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克在9月25日前就川普尋求立即將其免職一事作出回應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自川普8月下旬宣布以抵押貸款欺詐為由將庫克免職以來，她一直繼續履職，並否認相關指控。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Supreme Court Doesn’t Immediately Act on Trump Bid to Fire Cook</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B9%E6%9C%8825%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-142058032.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-20 00:15:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國眾議院通過共和黨撥款法案 參議院表決料陷入僵局",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"US House Speaker Mike Johnson\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ntubVBaRP9HAKc8P5kjzHg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/03158de7b55b3eda12a740ce65c4bed6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">US House Speaker Mike Johnson</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國眾議院通過臨時撥款法案，以避免政府在10月1日停擺，當天稍晚時段參議院將對法案進行表決，預計民主黨可能因為其中未包含他們要求的醫保支出條款而阻撓法案通過。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">眾議院議長邁克·約翰遜頂住部分共和黨人的抱怨，最終以217票對212票通過這項臨時撥款法案。幾乎所有民主黨眾議員都投下反對票。少數黨領袖Hakeem Jeffries表示，這項法案是「在捍衛美國人醫保與向唐納德·川普屈服之間做出的選擇」。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3839c74a-0367-3974-a317-cc04cbbe2033-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國眾議院議長邁克·約翰遜攝影師：Al Drago/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/k14PTKi71LTwl_yBVaLcPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a779a34be3f085ab8028ae1163a67913\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國眾議院議長邁克·約翰遜攝影師：Al Drago/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">參議院預計在周五稍晚對眾議院版本和民主黨領袖查克·舒默提出的替代法案同時進行表決，後者將把政府資金延長至10月31日。但兩項法案預計都無法表決通過。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題House Passes GOP Funding Bill, Sets Up Senate Shutdown Showdown</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jack Fitzpatrick、Ken Tran、Maeve Sheehey.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%A2%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%A2%E8%A1%A8%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%99%E9%99%B7%E5%85%A5%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80-153913544.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-20 01:20:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐盟提議從2027年起全面禁止進口俄羅斯液化天然氣 較原計畫提前一年",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"635\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e7zQUr6BzesCSMSeZqgkpQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e8a7d048dc07a4c940d7b501444edd45\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐盟提議自2027年1月1日起全面禁止進口<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:俄羅斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/俄羅斯\">俄羅斯</a>液化天然氣，作為其最新制裁措施的一部分，旨在削弱俄羅斯總統弗拉基米爾·普丁發動對烏克蘭戰爭的能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟還提議對更多俄羅斯銀行和金融機構實施全面交易禁令，並對中國和印度的相關實體實施貿易限制，這些實體曾協助莫斯科繞過歐盟的制裁。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前，美國總統唐納德·川普呼籲歐盟加強對俄羅斯能源貿易施壓。歐盟原計畫到2027年底逐步淘汰俄羅斯化石燃料。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"烏爾蘇拉·馮德萊恩攝影師：西蒙·沃爾法特/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BWp8qS0nD5QLln5UZIF8sA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e21c4b4a09b86731b73e9bba12846bf6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">烏爾蘇拉·馮德萊恩攝影師：西蒙·沃爾法特/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟委員會主席烏爾蘇拉·馮德萊恩周五在布魯塞爾對記者表示，「俄羅斯正充分表現出其對外交和國際法的蔑視。普丁總統屢屢升級局勢 —— 作為回應，歐洲將加大施壓力度。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0631f2b2-9460-354f-90c0-419bcc6a2285-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據歐盟統計局匯編的數據，歐盟每月從俄羅斯進口約5億至7億歐元液化天然氣。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"635\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LAj9IHquVpBdeL2bLb9kLQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5502e87b993be96149414432cd036ac2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU Proposes Full Ban on Russian LNG From 2027, a Year Early (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Katharina Rosskopf、Max Ramsay、Andrea Palasciano、Priscila Azevedo Rocha、John Ainger.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E6%8F%90%E8%AD%B0%E5%BE%9E2027%E5%B9%B4%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%B6%B2%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3-%E8%BC%83%E5%8E%9F%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D-%E5%B9%B4-145518035.html",
